[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Adds four new craftable scythes — Adamant, Mithril, Sunite, and Glorite — with scaling damage and attack speed to fill out the late-game tool tree.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Adamant, Mithril, Sunite[/b] — crafted at the Anvil. Each tier costs more and hits harder than the last.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Glorite[/b] — top-tier scythe, crafted at the Monster Anvil.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Damage and attack speed scale[/b] — both increase per tier, so the upgrade actually feels meaningful in combat as well as harvest speed.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Skill-gated[/b] — each scythe needs the appropriate combat skill level to wield, same gating the vanilla weapons follow.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/199]Auto Tools[/url] — automatically swaps to the right tool, including these scythes when you're standing next to grass or crops.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/224]More Jewelry[/url] — six extra jewelry slots stack nicely with the higher-tier scythes for stat builds.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — quick-save before testing a fresh scythe in combat.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — required by this mod; keeps everything loaded between play sessions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

